; COMMENTS
; UH-1 HUEY HF ANTENNA ONLY
; Single HF whip antenna for long-range tactical communication
;
; HF Whip Antenna (W028) Details:
; - Position: Belly-mounted, center fuselage (0.0m, 0.0m, -0.8m to -3.6m)
